tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished sixth at the Florida Q-School. Shot rounds of 67-69-70-63...T15 at the Tour's second tournament of the season, the Bayview Place Island Savings Open...Finished T9 at the Staal Foundation Open in Thunder Bay.
tourBios.personal: Best golf memory is winning back-to-back-to-back pro tournaments...Hopes to play Cypress Point someday...Big Dallas Cowboys and Oklahoma City Thunder fan...Dream foursome would include Ben Crenshaw, Tiger Woods and Arnold Palmer.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T9th in 2015 at the Staal Foundation Open presented by Tbaytel.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 67th in Scoring Average (Actual) on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
